{"tid":1561082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！23歲失蹤男秀茂坪墮樓亡！","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T14:38:33.000Z","uid":31166,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"d48be30d959d745b2cb71137e37fc4a83aec6fdb","tid":1561082,"uid":31166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"[size=4]23歲男子朱植雄前日（9日）上午離開秀茂坪秀明道的住所後便告失蹤，其家人同日向警方報案。至今早（11日）11時24分，警方接報，一名男子倒臥於秀茂坪邨秀義樓一天井，救護人員到場證實男子已告不治，現場沒有遺書。警方經調查後，確認死者為朱植雄，相信他從上址天台墮下，事件沒[有可疑，其死因仍有待驗屍後確定。/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190911/s00001/1568192243972/23%e6%ad%b2%e5%a4%b1%e8%b9%a4%e7%94%b7%e7%a7%80%e8%8c%82%e5%9d%aa%e5%a2%ae%e6%a8%93%e4%ba%a1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568192243972%2F23%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e8%25b9%25a4%25e7%2594%25b7%25e7%25a7%2580%25e8%258c%2582%25e5%259d%25aa%25e5%25a2%25ae%25e6%25a8%2593%25e4%25ba%25a1&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4oka%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=064ad75e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568192243972%2F23%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e8%25b9%25a4%25e7%2594%25b7%25e7%25a7%2580%25e8%258c%2582%25e5%259d%25aa%25e5%25a2%25ae%25e6%25a8%2593%25e4%25ba%25a1&h=ce938270\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190911/s00001/1568192243972/23%e6%ad%b2%e5%a4%b1%e8%b9%a4%e7%94%b7%e7%a7%80%e8%8c%82%e5%9d%aa%e5%a2%ae%e6%a8%93%e4%ba%a1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每日發現屍體，每日都話冇可疑</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" cla